      },
      "message": "hnerv_muon_lc: schema-repack + per-pair latent corrections on @AaronLeslie138's HNeRV\n\nBit-exact re-pack of hnerv_muon (PR #95) with schema-driven INT8 codec\n(~480 B saved) plus a 612 B per-pair latent-correction sidecar that\nperturbs single dims to minimize joint SegNet+PoseNet distortion.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
